media:description:

The Florida-born and Cali-raised producer and songwriter learned his trade from industry heavyweights Scott Storch, Rico Love, and Pierre Medor. With this level of education, it only made sense to collaborate with some of the most recognized artists in #HipHop: Rick Ross, Post Malone, French Montana, KSI, Lil Durk, King Von, Tee Grizzley, and Big Boi (to name a few).
